# Azazel (Yellow-Eyed Demon) - Dialogue File

@greeting
Azazel: Well, well... the Winchester boys.
Azazel: You have no idea what's coming.
Azazel: I've got plans for your brother, Dean.
Dean: You son of a bitch.

@threat
Azazel: You can't stop what's already in motion.
Azazel: Your daddy couldn't. And neither can you.
Sam: Watch us.
Azazel: Oh, I will. With great interest.

@final
Azazel: This isn't over, Winchesters.
Azazel: Not by a long shot.
Dean: We'll be ready.
Sam: Count on it.
